column5: Real DC power in KW

Seconds of run time remaining when low run time (UPS-Link's low battery) will be signaled on the local UI.  Under certain conditions  e.g.  on battery  when the run time is less than or equal to this value  the SimpleSignaling Status_BF.ShutdownImminent bit will be set.  The local UI should indicate this condition in the same manner as any shutdown pending.  Default should be Smart-UPS 3G/4G's default low battery warning of 150 seconds (2-3 min).  This value should always be greater than the SimpleTurnOffCountdownSetting when simple signalling is being used. A value of 0 indicates disabled.
The number of seconds until power will go out when running on battery.  This should never be compared as an actual value  but should be compared as LTE.
